{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "e004a2f0-54a9-4c64-87ed-1742c05ed573", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e004a2f0-54a9-4c64-87ed-1742c05ed573@1.pkg/1772602211175/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602211662", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e004a2f0-54a9-4c64-87ed-1742c05ed573@1.pkg/1772602211175/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602211662"}, "identifier": "e004a2f0-54a9-4c64-87ed-1742c05ed573", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>语言夸张不对，表现作者一心向学，而不是暗讽读书人。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列分析有误的一项是（ &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下列分析有误的一项是（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e004a2f0-54a9-4c64-87ed-1742c05ed573@1.pkg/item.json?v=1746000653084", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>第①段从借书，从师，衣食等方面讲述了作者年少时求学的艰难经历。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>作者采用现身说法，以自己的切身体会来劝勉马生更加刻苦向学。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>文中描写作者向&ldquo;先达&rdquo;求教的场面，语言夸张，暗讽当时读书人热衷功名。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>除宋濂之外，古人还有许多勤奋学习的事例，如匡衡凿壁偷光，车胤囊萤苦读等。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列分析有误的一项是（ &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "e004a2f0-54a9-4c64-87ed-1742c05ed573", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列分析有误的一项是（  ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列分析有误的一项是（ &nbsp;）</span></p></div>"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "cu